    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's interesting how u phrased that. when u say it \"ultimately forced\" the laws to pass, it sounds like a pretty straight line from the protests to the legislation. was it really just about the nonviolent stuff working, or were there other factors that caused the change?",
